Class UserViewController

  • java.lang.Object
    • controllers.UserViewController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LogoutEvent

    public class UserViewController
extends java.lang.Object
implements LogoutEvent
    This class controls the user's album summary page as represented in userview.fxml. Shows a list of all albums in the user's account. Implements LogoutEvent.
    Author:
    Derek Schatel
